text.text:
Let go of space or press the
opposite direction to wall jump

Hold C to open the inventory
Left or right click weapons to dual wield

Press ESCAPE to change: 
Name
Color
Volume
Hold S while moving to slide

Equip the Whip weapon
to grapple to Green objects

Hold W to heal
and to slow fall

While on the ground
Press R to reset
or Press T to go Home
